post-messages: [
  "hipjit needs the AMD HIP runtime and hiprtc libraries at build and run time; these are provided through the conf-hip package, which resolves the SDK, exports HIP_PATH, and puts the SDK's bin directory on PATH via opam's environment. Load the opam environment -- e.g. `eval $(opam env)`, or its PowerShell equivalent -- so the amdhip64/hiprtc libraries are found."
]
